properties.scriptMethodHeader: def apply(spark: SparkSession, in: DataFrame) : Script = {

expression.expression:
when(
    when((lit(Config.FEED_ARRIVAL_PUB_SCHEDULE) === lit("daily")).and(
           datediff(col("right.file_date"), col("left.last_processed_db_file_date")) =!= lit(1)
         ),
         lit(1)
    ).when(
        (lit(Config.FEED_ARRIVAL_PUB_SCHEDULE) === lit("weekly")).and(
          (datediff(col("right.file_date"), col("left.last_processed_db_file_date")) < lit(0))
            .or(datediff(col("right.file_date"), col("left.last_processed_db_file_date")) >= lit(10))
        ),
        lit(1)
      )
      .when(
        (lit(Config.FEED_ARRIVAL_PUB_SCHEDULE) === lit("monthly")).and(
          (ceil(months_between(col("right.file_date"), col("left.last_processed_db_file_date"), false)) > lit(1))
            .or(months_between(col("right.file_date"), col("left.last_processed_db_file_date"), false) < lit(0))
        ),
        lit(1)
      )
      .otherwise(lit(0)) === lit(1),
    
      concat(
        lit("ERROR: Out of sequence DB detected. Last Processed DB is <"),
        col("left.last_processed_db"),
        lit(">. Expected DB is <"),
        regexp_replace(col("left.last_processed_db"), lit("\\d*.db"), lit("")),
        when(
          when((lit(Config.FEED_ARRIVAL_PUB_SCHEDULE) === lit("daily")).and(
                 datediff(col("right.file_date"), col("left.last_processed_db_file_date")) =!= lit(1)
               ),
               lit(1)
          ).when(
              (lit(Config.FEED_ARRIVAL_PUB_SCHEDULE) === lit("weekly")).and(
                (datediff(col("right.file_date"), col("left.last_processed_db_file_date")) < lit(0))
                  .or(datediff(col("right.file_date"), col("left.last_processed_db_file_date")) >= lit(10))
              ),
              lit(1)
            )
            .when(
              (lit(Config.FEED_ARRIVAL_PUB_SCHEDULE) === lit("monthly")).and(
                (ceil(months_between(col("right.file_date"), col("left.last_processed_db_file_date"), false)) > lit(1))
                  .or(months_between(col("right.file_date"), col("left.last_processed_db_file_date"), false) < lit(0))
              ),
              lit(1)
            )
            .otherwise(lit(0)) === lit(1),
          when(
            (lit(Config.FEED_ARRIVAL_PUB_SCHEDULE) === lit("daily")).and(
              datediff(col("right.file_date"), col("left.last_processed_db_file_date")) =!= lit(1)
            ),
            date_add(to_date(col("left.last_processed_db_file_date"), "yyyyMMdd"), lit(1))
          ).when(
              (lit(Config.FEED_ARRIVAL_PUB_SCHEDULE) === lit("weekly")).and(
                (datediff(col("right.file_date"), col("left.last_processed_db_file_date")) < lit(0))
                  .or(datediff(col("right.file_date"), col("left.last_processed_db_file_date")) >= lit(14))
              ),
              date_add(to_date(col("left.last_processed_db_file_date"), "yyyyMMdd"), lit(7))
            )
            .when(
              (lit(Config.FEED_ARRIVAL_PUB_SCHEDULE) === lit("monthly")).and(
                (ceil(months_between(col("right.file_date"), col("left.last_processed_db_file_date"), false)) > lit(1))
                  .or(months_between(col("right.file_date"), col("left.last_processed_db_file_date"), false) < lit(0))
              ),
              date_add_months(col("left.last_processed_db_file_date"), 1)
            )
            .otherwise(lit(null))
        ).otherwise(lit(null)).cast(StringType),
        lit(">. But received DB is <"),
        col("right.source_extract_instance_directory"),
        lit(">")
      ).cast(StringType)
    
  ).otherwise(lit(""))

coalesce(when(col("seconds_since_directory_updated") < lit("900"), concat(lit("Source File is not stable (Possibly Still Extracting): "), col("source_extract_file_name"), lit(" for "), col("file_date"))).otherwise(when(col("size").cast(LongType) === lit(0), concat(lit("Source File has no data (Possibly Still Extracting): "), col("source_extract_file_name"), lit(" for "), col("file_date")))), lit(null).cast(StringType))
